OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry evening with long sunny spells.
OL,7,FThe night will remain dry with clear
OL,8,Fskies. Winds remaining light and
OL,9,Fturning quite chilly by dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA dry day with some good
OL,12,Fspells of sunshine. Cloudier in the
OL,13,Fmorning in the north around Angus,
OL,14,Fwith a cloudier period possible around
OL,15,Fthe middle of the day also.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FIt will
OL,18,Fbe a dry few days with variable cloud
OL,19,Fand some sunny spells. Mainly light
OL,20,Fwinds, and turning warmer on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
